data.description: English style lake front Georgia colonial with perfect placement on amazing Lake Pehlam. Privacy abounds on 8 acres with 5 bedrooms and three full baths and a half bath.  By the lake. Nice sized rooms and original floor plan. New windows, roof, flooring, heating, pool pump, and A/C both units. Decking boards replaced, new paint throughout, new rear ramp. Both upstairs bathrooms remodeled, new carpet thru out upstairs bedrooms. New paint throughout.
data.whatILove: The tranquility of the setting makes you feel like you are miles from anyone, but you are just minutes to shopping. Sit around the campfire, go fishing or kayak all over Lake Pelham.
